{"tid":2360377,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"寒獄獨囚黎智英，𡁻魷魚絲孤伶伶","createTime":"2021-01-09T16:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T04:06:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"91f7d60f9f717f97205e742744f6df666ab0cc20","tid":2360377,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T16:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/i4lLsHwhaaMiNzUty3pL_w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/mUKdmzP1yitUacXEQyX8LQ--~B/aD00MDA7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/4b96f508768486101e1216ef6363bc8f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fi4lLsHwhaaMiNzUty3pL_w--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FmUKdmzP1yitUacXEQyX8LQ--~B%2FaD00MDA7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F4b96f508768486101e1216ef6363bc8f&h=c53f59e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎智英在荔枝角收押所獨囚。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】壹傳媒黎智英被控欺詐及違反《港區國安法》，其保釋決定被終審法院批出終審上訴許可，黎於上月31日被押返荔枝角收押所獨囚。昨日是黎繼續收押的第8日，其妻子李韻琴及及幼子黎順恩帶同魷魚絲及牛肉乾等零食，結伴前往收押所探監。由於本港寒冷天氣警告正生效，相信他要在收押所內捱凍食魷魚絲。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英還押多日，其家人輪流到訪院所見面。李韻琴及黎順恩昨早約9時就到達荔枝角收押所，黎順恩手持零食探訪，兩人神情嚴肅，未有接受訪問就進入院所排隊。相隔約1小時後，兩人步出院所，李韻琴離開時架着黑色太陽眼鏡，並挽着黎順恩手臂離開，但同樣未有交代黎智英和探訪期間時情況。<br />\n<br />\n非法集結案 下月16日審<br />\n<br />\n73歲的黎智英被控欺詐及違反港區國安法中「勾結外國或者境外勢力危害國家安全」罪，兩案均會在今年4月16日於西九龍法院再訊。他另涉及前年和去年共4宗與未經批准集結的案件，其中一宗未經批准集結案早前在區院進行非公開的審前覆核，而該案將按原定時間表，於下月16日開審，預計審期10天。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/j13gzzrts0D7rRA1SB9Ibw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/619a46ea369f09442137e46faf763206\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fj13gzzrts0D7rRA1SB9Ibw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F619a46ea369f09442137e46faf763206&h=cbd15f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎智英妻兒帶同魷魚絲到收押所探訪黎智英。"},{"pid":"5f52d8e30b7d507e1363c8892b13a6e1e48111f9","tid":2360377,"uid":14422,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T16:41:08.000Z","msg":"唔通好似百份報腦細食白粉咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17dc840c35029a618e783522b2e9cdc2398a900b","tid":2360377,"uid":7656,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T16:41:28.000Z","msg":"鹿X珍700噸鴉片慢慢嘆，棄保潛逃，最後客死異鄉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a34240083b282cbe4da2d7ef2d1918d2c58ade4","tid":2360377,"uid":103156,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T16:47:15.000Z","msg":"白粉佬後人靠食汚糟錢過世"},{"pid":"29cf36a0a22e3c3b78a9b24249cd130275feae3a","tid":2360377,"uid":271395,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T17:09:45.000Z","msg":"d小食同天氣有咩關係"},{"pid":"b6bd3e4bb4cfa879e0a9b87755bf06a1beba8786","tid":2360377,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T19:15:58.000Z","msg":"相信他要在收押所內捱凍食魷魚絲。<br />\n睇錯 凍食魷魚絲"},{"pid":"f4e7112b12334b890c401e330ca1306be403f98d","tid":2360377,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T19:22:05.000Z","msg":"有魷魚絲食幾溫馨<br />\n一家人團聚都好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實呢幅圖係咪熱狗整既？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pifWqab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpifWqab.jpg&h=60000ae3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a2cc3ad12250c72f250a4a90b6b762b0146e4f3","tid":2360377,"uid":364767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f52d8e30b7d507e1363c8892b13a6e1e48111f9","tid":2360377,"uid":14422,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T16:41:08.000Z","msg":"唔通好似百份報腦細食白粉咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T19:25:29.000Z","msg":"東方左報賣白粉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkg